Serves 2-4 people 
1 small eggplant
1small zucchini
3 cloves of garlic
½ a bunch of fresh basil , (15g)
1 teaspoon dried oregano
1 teaspoon dried chilli flakes
olive oil
1 tablespoon baby capers
1 tablespoon red wine vinegar
1 x 400 g tin of good quality plum tomatoes
320 g dried wholewheat spaghetti
50 g pecorino/Parmesan or ricotta cheese (for non-vegans) 
extra virgin olive oil

node.text: Hi guys! I realize I never really talk about things that are very personal to me, so I thought in this video I would share a little bit about my modelling journey and my struggle with alcoholism and addiction and how it wasn’t until I decided to accept the help offered to me and do the work on myself that I ended up with a life I never dared to dream of. I hope this video can inspire you to not feel ashamed of asking for help if you are going through something similar, and know that you are not alone, whatever you are going through. All my Love and strength❤️

node.title: A day at a shoot and my modelling story!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by elsa hosk on July 28, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
Just checking in, how are you guys? 
I’m good. A little tired. Small headache. So in love with my baby Tuuli that my heart hurts sometimes. Spending most of my time with her. Excited about work! trying to stay inspired and surround myself with beauty. Counting the days until our family can come visit. Longing for an empty beach and tropical rain... beating myself up for not having time or energy to do things like working out, or cooking proper food more often. Working on being kinder to myself and others. I love you guys❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by elsa hosk on July 28, 2021. May be an image of table, sofa and living room.

node.text:
Sitting pretty✨
Two of my favorite makeup products ever. 
- “la lumiere” ,a highly pigmented highlighter powder that contains 96% natural ingredients, the first natural highlighter enriched with hyaluronic acid which hydrates the skin and sculpts the face for a healthy, luminous complexion. 
- Les Ombres Tage , a versatile eyeshadow/contour palette  formulated without microplastic, talc or silicone and not tested on animals. An infusion of ultra-concentrated pigments, which allows you an intense, buildable result, from the very first application, using your fingers or a brush. The must haves in your makeup bag! Comes in a lilac or lime green upcycled leather case exclusive to my @laboucherougeparis collab. 
Shop via link in bio✨

To celebrate my first makeup collection with @laboucherougeparis , we are giving one of you the chance to win a lipstick set from my collaboration!

Here is how to enter the giveaway:
• Like this post
• Follow both @hoskelsa and @laboucherougeparis
• Tag a friend in the comments
• Boost your chance to win by sharing this post in your stories

As a gift, the winner will receive the Lime Green set composed of the lime green lipstick leather case engraved with your initials and either Le Rouge Elsa or Le Nude Elsa refill  lipstick refill.

Terms & Conditions:
• Giveaway ends Friday July 30, 2021 at 11:59PM CT
• Winner will be contacted via DM
• Worldwide applications allowed
• Must be 13+ to enter

Good luck💞💖💕

node.text:
My red lipstick, Le Rouge Elsa, is the ultimate sexy orangey-red for summer. I imagined the perfect bright red hue for a hot summer night.. just throw on a white shirt or a little black dress and you’d be the chicest in the room❤️
The formula is infused with 93% natural origin ingredients such as hydrating hyaluronic acid for the best level of comfort it’s the most gorgeous feeling on your lips. 
 
Link in bio to shop. Limited edition, no restock. 
 
#elsahoskxlaboucherouge #elsahosk #lerougeelsa #laboucherouge #sustainableluxury

node.text:
Unboxing my summer essentials for @laboucherougeparis 

The small collection consists of 5 items: two exclusive lipstick shades Le Nude Elsa and Le Rouge Elsa, the perfect nude and orangey-red, a highlighter, a versatile eyeshadow/contour palette and a mascara, all refillable and housed in upcycled leather cases crafted by French artisans in my favorite colors this season: a pastel lilac and an vibrant lime green. 
 
A portion of proceeds from this collaboration will be going to Every Mother Counts (@everymomcounts), a non-profit dedicated to making pregnancy and childbirth safe for every mother, everywhere.
 
Shop #ELSAHOSKXLABOUCHEROUGE now via the link in my bio. Limited quantity. No restock. #laboucherouge #elsahosk #sustainableluxury

Video by the amazing @kulikulikulik @ruslanpelykh 🔫💚
